02:30.370 --> 02:53.300
one I remember was in,

02:30.370 --> 02:53.300
what would you call it, about

02:30.370 --> 02:53.300
genes in people and animals. See, I'd take a bunch 
of courses about cattle even chickens and things

02:59.733 --> 03:04.339
like that. We had to do that and rinse with the 
cattle. And then, what do you call it? They had a

03:17.274 --> 03:21.579
special, they did nothing but teach that. 
Genetics? Genetics. genetics. And I enjoyed

03:27.411 --> 03:28.493
that. I enjoyed that. Did you ever have a chemistry 
course from M.T. Harrington? No, I had it from...

03:33.600 --> 03:38.887
